"Per avviare <app>Software Center</app>, fare clic su <link "
"href=\"apt:cheese\">questo collegamento</link>."

#: C/app-cheese.page:27(item/p)
msgid ""
"Read the information and reviews about Cheese to make sure you want to "
"install it."
